article_text:
Kyle Smith, writing in the New York Post, Aug. 10:

One of these words is not like the others (or maybe they're all pretty much the same — you make the call): Loon, nutjob, crank, wingnut, whackjob, cuckoo, crackpot, dingbat, wacko,...

twitter.description: The liberal conceit that everyone on the right is crazy.
